title: On-Chain Data with PlanB and Willy Woo - Episode 8
description:
Lead Insights Analyst Will Clemente discusses the evolution of the Bitcoin market, cycles, and on-chain data with independent researcher PlanB and author of Bitcoin forecast Willy Woo for our weekly interview Podcast/YouTube channel series. Special thanks to both guests.

Plan B's Twitter: twitter.com/100TrillionUSD

Willy Woo's Twitter: twitter.com/woonomic

Will Clemente's Twitter: twitter.com/WClementeIII
